BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:64IavtrG7JTzIOA2hi24t
SUMMARY:Improv Greenhouse
DTSTAMP:20260327T022503Z
DTSTART:20260408T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to be surprised\\\, delighted\\\, and maybe even see 
	your wildest idea take on a life of its own!\\n\\n\\n\\nGraduate Greenhous
	e is a Wednesday night showcase featuring alumni from Unexpected Productio
	ns Improv School. Each performance highlights a different alumni group\\\,
	 putting their training to the test with unpredictable scenes\\\, various 
	formats\\\, and improvised stories. From long-form storytelling to charact
	er work\\\, these performers explore the boundaries of improv. \\nJan 7 Ma
	rket Improv \\nJan 14 \\nJan 21 \\nBut the fun doesn’t stop there! Stick a
	round for a double feature as we roll into Seattle’s longest-running Impro
	v Open Mic: the Duos Open Mic! Starting at 8:00 pm\\\, this weekly showcas
	e promises even more laughs\\\, surprises\\\, and improv magic.\n\nhttps:/
	/www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/graduate-greenhouse-fka-an-improvised
	-holiday-special-2-2-2/2026-04-08/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/graduate-greenhouse-fka-an-
	improvised-holiday-special-2-2-2/2026-04-08/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
